\c 28
\s Njere ndedzaMwari ega
\p
\v 1 Zvirokwazvo pane mugodhi wesirivha\x + 27.16.\x*, nenzvimbo yegoridhe\x + 28.6.\x* pavanonatsa\x + Mara. 3.3. 1 Makor. 28.18.\x*.
\v 2 Simbi inotorwa muvhu, nendarira inonyunguduswa \add pa\add*bwe\x + 29.6.\x*.
\v 3 Anotarira rima mugumo, uye anotsvakisisa kusvika pakuperera kwese\x + 11.7.\x*, mabwe erima\x + 10.22.\x* nemumvuri werufu\x + 3.5.\x*.
\v 4 Anopamura mugodhi kure nepanogara \add vanhu\add*, vanokanganikwa nerutsoka; vanorembera vachizeya uku nekuku \add kure\add* nevanhu\x + Det. 31.21. Map. 31.12.\x*.
\v 5 Nyika, mairi munobuda zvekudya\x + Map. 104.14.\x*, uye pasi payo pashanduka kuita semoto\x + 41.30.\x*.
\v 6 Mabwe ayo inzvimbo\x + 28.1.\x* yesafuri\x + 28.16. Eki. 24.10.\x*, uye ine guruva regoridhe.
\v 7 Nzira gondo raisingazivi, neziso rerukodzi\x + Rev. 11.14. Det. 14.13.\x* harina kuiona\x + 20.9.\x*.
\v 8 Imbwanana dzinozvikudza hadzina kuitsika\x + 41.34.\x*; shumba inotyisa haina kupfuura nepo\x + 10.16.\x*.
\v 9 Anotandavadzira ruoko rwake pabwe rakaoma, anopidigura makomo nemidzi \add yawo\add*.
\v 10 Anopamura migero pamabwe; neziso rake rinoona chose chinokosha\x + Isa. 33.21.\x*.
\v 11 Anosunga nzizi dzirege kuvhinza\x + Isa. 33.21.\x*; nezvakavanzika anobudisira pachiedza\x + 11.6. Map. 44.21.\x*.
